{"tid":666592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墮倫敦金騙案　14人危站追數","createTime":"2018-05-16T04:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T05:56:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b97b64631a15af3926161daa2b9441152071589","tid":666592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180516/20392329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F20392329&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c03ec35b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F20392329&h=6c7436db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180516/20392329</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月16日 <br />\n<br />\n墮倫敦金騙案　14人危站追數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180516/large/16la8p511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F16la8p511.jpg&h=d41ca4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有內地人昨危站九龍城豪宅的天台，要求見涉騙財投資公司負責人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】14名內地男女懷疑早前在本港一個網上平台購買倫敦金後發現受騙，一行人來港向涉事的投資公司姓林負責人追討損失。他們根據公司查冊紀錄，昨晨9時許闖入該公司負責人報住位於九龍城衙前圍道51號豪宅陶源的地址，他們穿上寫有「倫敦金詐騙」的背心，在場拉起橫額抗議。至中午12時，其中14人突然繞過保安衝入大廈直奔天台危站，保安員報警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱3,000人失900萬<br />\n<br />\n警員及消防員趕到現場，警隊談判專家亦奉召到場游說，當中有11人先後返回安全位置，但有2男1女一直堅持要見到負責人才罷休，3人與談判專家持續拉鋸至晚上截稿時仍未解決。他們聲稱得知被騙苦主至少3,000人，合共損失約900萬元。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦金騙局無日無之，中台澳三地四名人士去年墮「美女」圈套跌入倫敦金騙局，4人透過手機交友程式或網上平台認識「美女」，對方介紹他們到本港一間投資公司開設買賣倫敦金戶口，結果合共被騙去逾500萬元。其中一名台灣苦主，在不足10個月被騙去400萬元。4人上月30日來港到禮賓府向特首請願及往灣仔警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n■記者詹家志  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n非禮女廚工　翠華主管判社服<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n物華街路陷被封　料今晚重開"},{"pid":"6964369dcc6d0437967721b31b680d1b9926fcdb","tid":666592,"uid":20658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"仲有人信先on9"},{"pid":"3ab9b09561b16113b11df848004b1a1699627931","tid":666592,"uid":12449,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"要輸得起 不能掉現眼"},{"pid":"2430e60ca365a38aac11dcf65fa1e65e2e609758","tid":666592,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"矛盾大對決"},{"pid":"e37dbba0ec3701ff3138e97c0014c350882308d9","tid":666592,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"他們聲稱得知被騙苦主至少3,000人，合共損失約900萬元。<br />\n除開每人損失3000蚊都要跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?btw,以我所知入場費至少都幾皮,應該報紙佬寫漏數"},{"pid":"5efdc717d457b4165cacc82c107c2042bd5baa49","tid":666592,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"危站？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7381289f042c1de03515586764e04032565c2138","tid":666592,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"寫漏數 九百萬咁少 夠班友吸血?"},{"pid":"7de544fe98763b6099a331894640f90dcee00cf6","tid":666592,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"姐係自殘 跟住叫人還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f40e14837189fda697d31abef26ad1c43fb9db9","tid":666592,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"係精神既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b88516cbd9d89ad21cf986a0fe89684cf1ac3d","tid":666592,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"MK金融仔又赢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}